entry --- MIDI text stream to Lilypond-style chord sequencer
draw --- translate render.rs output into Nuklear/Xlib drawing primitives
g2ly --- convert group output into a four-staff LilyPond score
group --- align MIDI notes to lesson bassline, figures, and melody
l2ly --- convert lesson file from stdin into minimal LilyPond grand staff
load --- load and normalize continuo lesson data
midi --- read MIDI input from device and output timed events
render --- render the LilyPond subset produced by g2ly
rules --- elegant voice-leading validation for figured bass
run --- execute a graph of interconnected processes
show --- display the primitive stream from draw in an X11 window
